    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>华丽动作 畅快战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/f1cbf2beeed006d9618fb029c8a9ca54.poster.avif?t=1770862049\" width=650 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/f1cbf2beeed006d9618fb029c8a9ca54.webm?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/f1cbf2beeed006d9618fb029c8a9ca54.mp4?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魅力十足的角色、风格强烈的美学呈现、极具张力的动作演出，造就超华丽帅气的战斗体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>连招构筑 极限操作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/784de511dd6103e39187134a19263378.poster.avif?t=1770862049\" width=650 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/784de511dd6103e39187134a19263378.webm?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/784de511dd6103e39187134a19263378.mp4?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >畅爽丝滑的操作、无限可能的连招、拳拳到肉的打击感，这或许是至今为止动作性最强的肉鸽游戏！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超多角色 豪华制作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/d5b3277bac83bf3bb46fc772135d7cb7.poster.avif?t=1770862049\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/d5b3277bac83bf3bb46fc772135d7cb7.webm?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/d5b3277bac83bf3bb46fc772135d7cb7.mp4?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12位极富个性的可选角色、各有独一无二的战斗方式、实力声优倾情演绎，呈现出魅力非凡的角色演出。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>百种招式 自由定制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/e64b91e694dc34c3bc38935d1054045b.poster.avif?t=1770862049\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/e64b91e694dc34c3bc38935d1054045b.webm?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/e64b91e694dc34c3bc38935d1054045b.mp4?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上百种招式自由构建、搭配海量元素效果、角色能力相互迭代传承，无限可能的战斗塑造出独属于你的最强斗士。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>命运抉择 拯救世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/76922ec4f371477ecd21cbdea546428d.poster.avif?t=1770862049\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/76922ec4f371477ecd21cbdea546428d.webm?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/76922ec4f371477ecd21cbdea546428d.mp4?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来的世界陷入灾变，人们进入名为“ACE”的赛博空间，寻求对抗危机的最后机会。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 如果这个世界只有你知道真相，你会如何应对？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >终点亦是起点，你的选择将决定人类的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>联动经典 全新体验</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/0bf0d00032dc3ab72962c555912b3f5b.poster.avif?t=1770862049\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/0bf0d00032dc3ab72962c555912b3f5b.webm?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273430/extras/0bf0d00032dc3ab72962c555912b3f5b.mp4?t=1770862049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情享受来自《艾希》与《死亡细胞》的免费经典IP联动。 <br>让「艾希」与旁白君再度重相逢，根据旁白君的指示开启一段旅程。<i>当然，你也可以不听他的：）</i> <br>或者化身「枭首者」，在类银河恶魔城的特制关卡中探索，发掘一段原创的全新故事；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >温馨提示：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >联动内容涉及剧情与原作并无关联。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  本游戏含有可能诱发光敏性癫痫的画面闪烁等视觉元素。</p></li></ul>",
